  "body": "The https://docs.perl6.org/syntax/unit says\r\n\r\n> This must be at the start of the file (preceded only by comments or use statements)\r\n\r\nHowever, it can also be preceded by `sub EXPORT` at the very least (which actually *has* to go outside the `unit` stuff). I filed [R#2020](https://github.com/rakudo/rakudo/issues/2020) to clarify what's allowed, and once that's resolved, it would go in to fix this issue.",
